data.description: Step into this meticulously kept home nestled in the private lake community of Scenic Lakes. Recently renovated, this 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath haven boasts numerous updates and upgrades. The newer eat-in kitchen showcases stunning granite countertops, all-new cabinetry, and stainless-steel appliances. Revel in the gorgeous flooring and elegant lighting throughout. With walkouts from both the kitchen and family room to a deck and covered patio, immerse yourself in the peacefulness and tranquility of the 1.41-acre property that backs up to a wildlife preserve. Scenic Lakes offers a wealth of amenities including swimming, fishing, hiking, and more. Just 50 miles from NYC and 15 minutes from Mountain Creek and Crystal Springs, indulge in spa days, skiing, and golfing. This pre-inspected home features a brand-new roof, gutters, washer and water heater, with the septic system quoted as being in "Perfect" condition. Boiler is 5yrs old. Propane Gas, tank is owned.  With tasteful furnishings available for sale, this home is truly move-in ready, offering the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Come out and see for yourself today!
